{
  "stem": "21437.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, you know we're not allowed to sing here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But she said, lean in my ear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I remember for the first time, she was on the left side, and I leaned forward, and I remember this going this way, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The feel of that number on my skin, and I sang into her ear two French songs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And from then on, I had to sing every night to her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "What were the two French songs?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Want me to sing them to you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SINGING IN FRENCH]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so it went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not the end of it, but, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- in the whisper, and so I sang to her in sort of very gently.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What it did to me was like an explosion, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It meant that I actually used my voice for singing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it's just-- it's indescribable what a human being can-- how much is there within us if we acknowledge this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From then on, through the last minute, through the last minute.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was there for between 13 and 14 months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In this camp, really, you know, we-- again, it was like in Oldenburg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was-- those two camps was the longest, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What effect did this-- this explosion-- when you sang the songs, what effect did it have on you?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was acknowledging my being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it-- I was a very young, again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- I sort of-- I-- I-- Like-- like in the-- like in Oldenburg, my body protested, you know, that my body needed to cleanse itself out because it locked itself out for self-preservation.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Apparently, you know, you needed-- you just-- you just-- you know, they can take everything away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what we whispered to each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
